milestones.description: Hamilton has scored 5 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Fraser Watts's record
Lionel Cann and Romaine's 134-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 68 between Clay Smith and Romaine
Hamilton and Ryan Watson's 106-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 56 between Hamilton and Fraser Watts
Romaine has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (17) for BMUDA, going past Tucker
Lionel Cann and Romaine's 134-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 98 between Romaine and Dean Minors

stories.title: Hussain reprimanded for dissent
stories.subTitle: Scotland v Bermuda, World Cricket League
stories.summary: Scotland's middle-order batsman, Omer Hussain, has been officially reprimanded for showing dissent at an umpire's decision during his country's five-wicket defeat against Bermuda at Nairobi in the World Cricket League
